org.jdom2.jaxb

Class JDOMStreamReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jdom2.output.support.AbstractOutputProcessor
      • org.jdom2.jaxb.JDOMStreamReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    XMLStreamConstants, XMLStreamReader

    public class JDOMStreamReader
extends org.jdom2.output.support.AbstractOutputProcessor
implements XMLStreamReader
    An XMLStreamReader implementation that reads the XML document out of a JDOM Document. The reader reads XML Events by walking the DOM tree, reporting all XML stream events as it encounters them in the DOM.
    Author:
    gordon burgett https://github.com/gburgett
